      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 16 obituary of British etiquette expert John Morgan, which misstated recommendation of his about birth announcements</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An obituary on Sunday about John Morgan, a British etiquette expert, misstated a recommendation of his that drew a columnist's criticism in The Guardian. Mr. Morgan endorsed birth announcements of heavy card stock cut from a sheet weighing 335 grams over all, approximately 11.8 ounces; it was not the announcements that were to weigh 335 grams.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
